    "millsfield:images_texts": [
      "Ski slopes\nby the bunch.\nHughes Airwest can fly you to more favorite\nslopes in the west than any other airline.\nJust look at some of our slopes: Sun Valley, Salt\nLake City, Banff, Tahoe, Big Mountain (Kalispell).\nMt. Bachelor (Redmond, Oregon), Schweitzer (Spo-\nkane), Vail, Aspen, Bogus Basin (Boise).\nFor reservations and information,\ncall a Travel Agent or your local\nHughes Airwest office. And\ndon't forget to ask about our\nski packages.\nTop Banana in the West.\nHughes Airwest.",
      "Hughes\nAirwest\nInternational and Domestic Flights\nJanuary 15,1978\nSun Mlles lasha\nTop Banana in the West"
    ],
